text:
Today, we're off for the day after this, right?
I have somewhere I'd like to go...

Ah okay.
Shall I come along?

I don't need you to.
You'll just make us stand out more anywway.

Somewhere you need to be undercover?
Where on earth...

In that case,
it doesn't seem like I would be of use anyway.

Even around here
there might be people that recognize your face, Fuyuko.

...that much is obvious.
Fuyu has no reason to let her guard down, right?
